        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "You were born in LA and you died in LA.  As a mortal you ran with a tight circle of artists, hackers, and activists that were just doing thier best to survive in a world inhospitable to human life and trying theirr best to get others to wake up to the wasteland before it was too late.   After the crash of 2008 you thought things were finally going to change.  You even hooked up with some preppers outside LA who were stockpiling for after the total collapse.  It was all coming together and then someone jumped you in an alley outside of a rave.  At first you thought you were fine but the bite on your neck kept getting worse and you knew you were a goner when the sun started to make your skin itch.  It only took a little time online to figure out you were a vampire and that you were not alone. You survived for years picking up tidbits about your nature online and learning who to avoid if you wanted to stay undead.  Now you know LA is getting crowded with vampires and you're going to have to leave or choose a side.  When you approached the Camarilla Gang of vampires you were pretty sure they'd try to kill you, but when they tested your blood they found out it was something special.  Maybe that's why you can go out during the day and you only get a nasty sunburn.."
        ],
